Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fight Emperor’s strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,could a Fight King shake it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Snake Spirit Gathering!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would actually fall here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who hurt her;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then leave your lives behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:44.50,Episode,,0,0,0,,{\fade(640,640)\pos(975,722)}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(460,160)\pos(1361.6,338.8)}Xiao Li
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(460,200)\pos(1720,348)}Xiao Ding
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fade(460,360)\pos(1454,420)}Xue Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On the Dou Qi Continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the gap between Qi Methods
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is determined by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}the degree to which the Qi vortex within the Qi center can accommodate Dou Qi;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,difference in Dou Qi quality;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of absorption of natural energy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and its refinement into Dou Qi during training;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the speed and ease of driving Dou Qi during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Qi Methods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,are split, from highest to lowest, into Tian, Di, Xuan, and Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When cultivation class is equal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,those who practice high class Qi Methods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,far surpass those who practice low class Qi Methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the class of the Qi Method you practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the benefits it brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your resilience to conquer the Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My family’s Young Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Misty Cloud Sect Leader, Yun Yun’s most prized disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she have trash for a husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,since you don’t want Uncle Xiao’s reputation damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,after three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,come to the Misty Cloud Sect to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,our engagement shall be annulled on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,must succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,can open up a special space inside your body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,used to store a Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,find a way to drive the flame seed into the Acceptance Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the Acceptance Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,how did it suddenly become this much stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Although refining a Heavenly Flame can raise one’s fighting strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it shouldn’t have the ability to increase cultivation class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Refining the Heavenly Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to have succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have changed quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All your wounds are healed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,my whole body is filled with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your full strength to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me sense which star you’ve currently reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve actually reached a Four-star Fight Master’s strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-star Fight Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After entering the empty-mind state,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,while in a trance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I saw the flame seed repairing the meridians inside my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that’s what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lucky fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to be a benefit of refining a Heavenly Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Refining a Heavenly Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,only after gradually becoming proficient at controlling it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will it bring you benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a short period of time, it shouldn’t cause any increase in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,first time I’ve seen something like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it’s a pity;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were a Fight Spirit or Fight King
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and still soared by several stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then you would really have profited big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m already satisfied with soaring to four stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was any higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,my body couldn’t adapt to this level of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,haven’t I relied on training one step at a time to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing when enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,try out your Origin Flame Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Lotus Core Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Xiao Yan, finally possess a Heavenly Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,now that I have a Heavenly Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,can I immediately start forging the Flame Mantra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is about balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Swallowing the Heavenly Flame tonight has already exhausted your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest for a day first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Mercenary Company has taken things too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapping Qing Lin in the middle of the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,do they think our Desert Metal no longer has any people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll immediately bring our men
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to go confront Luo Bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Mercenary Company’s strength has skyrocketed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Apart from that Fight Grandmaster Luo Bu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,another Fight Grandmaster has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of Rock Desert City’s medium-sized mercenary groups
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,have just been cleaned up by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we at Desert Metal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,aren’t cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Company Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Xue Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Xue Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Mercenary Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They surrounded our compound
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and spouted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that in one day’s time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don’t submit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they would make Desert Metal a bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Luo Bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The air temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has already reached its lowest point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now is the coolest time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}Although it’ll provide little help in using the Heavenly Flame to forge the Flame Mantra,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we can’t just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When forging the Flame Mantra,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am unable to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only person who practices the Flame Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1072)}Whether it possesses the qualifications and potential befitting of a Tian Class Qi Method,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all of that, you have to gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what the scroll said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to evolve this Qi Method,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you must continually swallow Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You already narrowly escaped death in swallowing the Green Lotus Core Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Flame Mantra is unable to evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,abandon this kind of Qi Method.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,now isn’t the time to say depressing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if trying to evolve the Flame Mantra fails this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I still won’t give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a necessity for me to become a strong practitioner at the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your new body
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be refined with the flame produced after evolving the Flame Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up on practicing the Flame Mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,would be giving up on your hopes of resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Disciple is not willing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and won’t give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you persist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my good disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,train in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you can succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this Qi Method is unable to evolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,will do everything possible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a peak practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Flame Mantra’s space?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only a Huang Class, Low Level Qi Method,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,yet it is already this imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Lotus Core Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,between heaven and earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the first Heavenly Flame to forge the Flame Mantra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Merge with the Flame Mantra into one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Green Lotus Core Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You once surrendered to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me in forging the Flame Mantra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Still trying to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Disobedient, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll force you to be obedient!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,how is it so powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,stinky brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget this bullshit Flame Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We are leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,try once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are getting yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never going to trust anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, accepting you as a disciple
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was only because I wanted to absorb your Dou Qi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and restore my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,why must you be this stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are actually willing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to court death for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it means losing this old life of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,as my disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you must hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your foundation will be damaged by the Green Lotus Core Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you merge with the Flame Mantra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Teacher’s only hope for resurrection!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Xiao Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve successfully proven that this Flame Mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,really can swallow Heavenly Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Its potential
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is indeed limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And your potential
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is also limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Xuan Class, Middle Level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Flame Mantra has increased by an entire class
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to the previous Huang Class Middle Level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is worthy of being the Green Lotus Core Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,able to supply such powerful energy for evolving the Qi Method.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But the process
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,was extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of agony was truly horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Heavenly Flame’s backlash succeeded back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even my spirit, I’m afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would have been incinerated to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This Flame Mantra is indeed strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows which madman invented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, we went through countless hardships
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to obtain this thing from that damned place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time remains
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,until that Three Year Agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nalan Yanran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These last two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you’d better get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the Flame Mantra continues to swallow Heavenly Flames
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and reaches Tian Class,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher will be able to be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai Bodong’s map of the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we must obtain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Snake People Shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to look for Sand Datura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinky brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn’t forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what’re we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s go find Hai Bodong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This stinky brat.
